            <p class="text-gray-600">Pemasangan express dan layanan bantuan teknis standby 24 jam.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-t-4 border-blue-600 hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">💰</div>
